Add the tracking code as soon as you can in your PHP script:

    require_once 'Bouncer/Bouncer.php';
    Bounce::run(array('namespaces' => array('siteid')));

To read the statistics, add the following code in a PHP file:

    require_once 'Bouncer/Bouncer.php';
    Bouncer::stats(array('namespace' => 'siteid'));
